title: Frank Zappa - Hammersmith Odeon (1978) 3CD (2010)
description:
Three hours of performances culled from live recordings from the series of 4 concerts played at Hammersmith Odeon in January and February 1978.
 
Much of the music would appear in different form on the album â€˜Sheik Yerbouti', 
but these cuts stand on their own merit.

Released in honor of FZ's 70th birthday and favorite holiday, Halloween.
